Denver 47 fair; Des Moines 55 fair; Indianapolis 57 cloudy; Kansas
City 59 fair; Little Rock 58 fair; Louisville 55 partly cloudy;
Memphis 65 cloudy; Nashville 56 fair; New Orleans 56 fair; North
