239-6200, same number as Telecharge. Ticketron. Available.
   _``Sid Caesar &amp; Company,'' the television comedian in a series
of revue sketches. Now in previews, opens Nov. 1. Golden, 239-6200,
same number as Telecharge. Available.
   _``Sweeney Todd,'' a revival of the Stephen Sondheim musical
